      • parseShortName

        public static XSDVocabulary parseShortName(String s)
        Easy parse of short names of the kind "xsd:typename". Note that the match must be exact - uppercase or lowercase variants are not accepted. An IllegalArgumentException will he thrown for non matching input.
        Parameters:
        s - string of the form xsd:typename
        Returns:
        the XSDVocabulary item matching xsd:typename, e.g., STRING for "xsd:string"
